data.title: Our Lady of the Miracles Cathedral, Kallianpur (Milagres Cathedral)
data.meta_description: The Cathedral of Our Lady of Miracles, Indo-Portuguese; Catedral de Nossa Senhora dos Milagres, is a Roman Catholic Cathedral situated at Kallianpur in the Udupi district of Karnataka, India.
data.text:
The Cathedral of Our Lady of Miracles,[1] Indo-Portuguese; Catedral de Nossa Senhora dos Milagres (formerly a parish church as the Church of Our Lady of Miracles, Portuguese: Igreja de Nossa Senhora dos Milagres), is a Roman Catholic Cathedral situated at Kallianpur in the Udupi district of Karnataka, India.

This article is about the Milagres Cathedral in Kallianpur, Udupi district. For the other Milagres Church in Hampankatta, see Milagres Church (Mangalore).
